name: ArcaneMix
description:
v1 was Arcane Diffusion V3 mixed with Stable Arcane v1 at 0.4

v2 is Arcane Diffusion V3, Stable Arcane v2 and v1, Artwork Arcane and Vi from Arcane mixed together, see version notes for percentages.

This model may be unnecessary as all the ones mixed into it were similar and great on their own, but I'm experimenting and just sharing what I come up with.

The trigger words for the base models were "Arcane Style" and "LeagueofStyle" so I most frequently used both or "mix of Arcane Style and LeagueofStyle".

modelVersions.name: ArcaneMix-v2
modelVersions.description:
Models used in arcanemix v2 =

Arcane Diffusion v3 (60%) https://huggingface.co/nitrosocke/Arcane-Diffusion + submix 3 (40%)

submix 3 = mix 2 (70%) + Stable Arcane v1 (30%) https://civitai.com/models/3446/stablearcane

submix 2 = mix 1 (70%) + Artwork Arcane (30%) https://huggingface.co/s3nh/artwork-arcane-stable-diffusion

submix 1 = Stable Arcane v2 (70%) https://civitai.com/models/3446/stablearcane + vi From Arcane v1 (30%) https://civitai.com/models/4/vi-from-arcane

example images untouched

use keywords "arcane style" and "leagueofstyle"
